    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and would be most appropriate for a buyer seeking a project car or a source for parts. The engine suffers from persistent oil leaks and an audible knock, while the transmission exhibits significant hesitation when shifting. Cosmetically, the exterior has several noticeable dents and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. It is not currently in reliable driving condition and is sold strictly as-is.",
