    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has several scratches and minor dings, and the paint shows some age. The interior is functional but has visible staining on the carpets and wear on the upholstery. Mechanical components are operational, though the car shows signs of significant use.",
